               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; incipit of Texts I-1 and I-2 and their sections; names of the donors; directives to the ministers; abbreviations of the directives yǝbǝl kahǝn “the priest says”, yǝbǝl diyaqon “the deacon says”, yǝbǝl ḥǝzb “the people say”; titles of books to be read; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
On the incipit pages of Text I-1 and 1-2 (fols. 2r, 26r), a few lines are rubricated (alternating with black lines).</rubric>
