                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note is written in the main hand, in a small and thin script. It mentions the name of the donor, Wälättä Giyorgis, and of the church which received the Ms., Qǝddus Yoḥannǝs Däbrä Betel Koholo (here Kokolo).
                        </item>
